<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Industrious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Industrious,</orth> zealous, studious: <cit><quote>my i. servant Ariel,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 33</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>they gape and point at your i. scenes and acts of death,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.376" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 376</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a true i. friend,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 62</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>put we on i. soldiership,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 4, 16</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>